title: Two Men Arrested for Fraudulent ATM Use and Theft (City of Irvine, CA)
text: ( Source : City of Irvine , CA) Irvine, CA (Oct. 6, 2016): The Irvine Police Department ( IPD ) arrested two men for fraudulently accessing ATMs to steal money after watching victims use their personal identification numbers (PINs). Cleo Charles
